SUMMARY:GTApreneurs March 31-2026 Business Networking Event Vaughan - Toronto
DESCRIPTION:Toronto Women in Business Networking Group (TWIB)\nJoin us at an exciting Business Networking Event in Vaughan (1 block north of Toronto) on Tuesday March 31 where you can meet potential clients and referral partners\, learn something new\, enjoy a meal and promote your business!\n\n**REGISTER HERE:** https://gtapreneurs.com/networking-events-vaughan\n\n**VENUE:** Improve Canada\, 2nd floor auditorium\n**ADDRESS:** 7250 Keele St\, Vaughan\, ON (Between Steeles Ave W. and 407)\n\n**PARKING:** Free\, onsite. Park on the NORTH SIDE of the building off of Snidercroft Rd\n\n**\\*\\*DIRECTIONS TO FIND THE ROOM:** Walk through entrance M\, go straight ahead until you get to the main aisle. Straight ahead will be a staircase. If you prefer to take the elevator\, make a right at the main aisle\, go down a few stores and you will see it on the left.\n\n**EVENT ITINERARY:**\n\n* **5:00-6:00pm:** Open networking\, food buffet\, visit exhibitor booths\n* **6:00-6:10pm:** GTApreneurs welcoming presentation\n* **6:10-6:30pm:** Guest Speaker Presentation\n* **6:30-7:00pm:** Exhibitor Introductions + member Elevator Pitches\n* **7:00-8:00pm:** Open networking\, visit exhibitor booths\n\n**MENU:** Pizza\, Veggies\, Fruit\, dessert and other snacks\n**BEVERAGES:** Pop and water\n\n**TICKETS**\n\n* **GTApreneurs' Referral Group\, Exhibitor and Mega Networking Members:** Free\n* **Non-members:** $27 in advance or $29 on event day\n\n***Not a GTApreneurs Member?*** Go here to view our memberships and register: https://gtapreneurs.com/business-networking-memberships\n\n**QUESTIONS ABOUT THE EVENT?**\n\nCall or text Tammy at (416) 522-7770 or info@gtapreneurs.com.\n\nTo learn about Tammy Defoe's business coaching services\, please go to https://gtapreneurs.com/about and https://gtapreneurs.com/business-coaching-toronto\n\n**EXHIBITORS:**\n\n* **Gorette Marques\,** Realty Executive Plus\, https://gmarquesrealtor.com\n* **Sonia Kurmey\,** Arbonne\, www.soniakurmey.arbonne.com\n* **Balbir Pabila\,** PPLSI\\~LegalShield\, https://bkpabila.legalshieldassociate.com\n* **Abhishek Basak\,** Clerk Tech\, www.clerk-tech.com\n* **Monica Hecht\,** The Village Hive\, www.thevillagehive.ca\n* **Ian McIntosh\,** DigiMinds Bots \\| Exhibitor Follow Up Pro\\\, [www.digimindscrm.com](www.digimindscrm.com)\n* **Brad Aylward\,** BHA Mortgage Corp. Mortgage Architects LIC # 12728\, www.bhamortgagecorp.com\n* **Adrian Newman\,** Numero Uno Web Solutions Inc.\, www.numerounoweb.com\n\n\\*Exhibitor tables available. Visit www.gtapreneurs.com/exhibitor to book a spot\n\n\\*We will EMAIL you the GUEST CONTACT SHEET the day after the event by 5pm. If you don't receive it in your inbox\, please check your SPAM/JUNK folder. Note: You must attend the event to receive the guest contact sheet.
