SUMMARY:GTApreneurs April 15-2026 Afternoon Virtual Business Networking Event Toronto
DESCRIPTION:Toronto Women in Business Networking Group (TWIB)\n\\*\\*You need to register on our website to attend this event and get the zoom link. RSVPing on Meetup does not mean that you are registered\, even though Meetup.com will send you an email saying that you have. Thank you. Please go here: https://gtapreneurs.com/networking-events-toronto\n\n\\*Please note this event is advertised on multiple platforms\, and we expect around 20-25 guests.\n\nDo you want more clients? Join us for GTApreneurs April 15-2026 Afternoon Virtual Business Networking Event to connect with other amazing entrepreneurs\, learn something new and promote your business!\n\n**WARM-UP ITINERARY:**\n\n* **[11:45am-12pm: Pre-event networking]**\n* **12:00-12:10pm:** GTApreneurs welcoming presentation\n* **12:10-12:30pm:** Featured Presentation: Tammy Defore\, ***“How Big is Your Sales Funnel?”***\n* **12:30-1:00pm:** Elevator Pitches (45 seconds each)\nFree\n\n**PREMIUM EVENT ITINERARY:**\n\n* **[11:45am-12pm: Pre-event networking]**\n* **12:00-12:10pm:** GTApreneurs welcoming presentation\n* **12:10-12:30pm:** Featured Presentation: Tammy Defore\, ***“How Big is Your Sales Funnel?”***\n* **12:30-1:00pm:** Elevator Pitches (45 seconds each)\n* **1:00-2:00pm:** Breakout rooms (Network 1-1 with other guests)\n\n**TICKETS**\n**GTApreneurs' Referral Group\, Exhibitor and Mega Networking Members:** Free\n**Non-members:** $10\n\\*Premium ticket includes Guest Contact sheet emailed to you after the event. Note: You must attend the event to receive the guest contact sheet.\n\nThis event will feature our President of GTApreneurs\, **Tammy Defoe**\, who excels at helping entrepreneurs get more exposure and more clients. She is a Business Coach and Consultant specializing in business development\, sales\, marketing\, digital marketing\, public speaking\, business communication and networking. If you would like 1-1 assistance for your business\, visit https://gtapreneurs.com/business-coaching-toronto to learn more about her services and book a free video call at https://gtapreneurs.zohobookings.ca/#/gtapreneursinc2 to talk about what you need to get your business moving in the right direction.\n\n**QUESTIONS?** Contact GTApreneurs at 416-522-7770 or info@gtapreneurs.com\n\nWant to attend the Premium version of our Virtual Networking Events for FREE? Become a Member. Learn more at https://gtapreneurs.com/business-networking-memberships\n\nWe look forward to seeing you at the event!\n\nGTApreneurs Team
