SUMMARY:GTApreneurs BizX 2026 Business Expo and Conference – VIP Ticket
DESCRIPTION:Toronto Women in Business Networking Group (TWIB)\nYou are invited to an exciting mega networking bash! Join us on **Tuesday\, October 20\, 2026** for **GTApreneurs’** **BizX 2026 Business Expo and Conference!** We expect 300+ small business owners and entrepreneurs all looking to meet you and many others to do business together!\n\n**REGISTER HERE** \\>\\> [https://gtapreneurs.com/bizx-2026-business-expo](https://gtapreneurs.com/bizx-2026-business-expo)\n\n**DOOR PRIZE RAFFLE:** Bring your business card and drop it in the box for a chance to win a great prize.\n\n**BIZX 2026 BUSINESS EXPO CONTEST:** Each time you visit an exhibitor\, and exchange business cards (or exchange information electronically)\, they will put a sticker on your event map. Fill your map with a sticker from every exhibitor to win a prize. At the end of the day (4:30-5:00pm)\, we will announce Expo Contest winners as well as guest door prize winners and exhibitor draw winners.\n\n**VIP TICKET ITINERARY:**\n\n* **9:00-10:30am:** Registration + Continental breakfast + Networking\n* **10:30-10:45am:** GTApreneurs welcoming presentation\n* **10:45-11:00am:** Platinum and Gold Sponsor Introductions\n* **11:00-11:20am:** Featured Speaker 1 presentation\n* **11:20-11:40am:** Featured Speaker 2 presentation\n* **11:40-12:00pm:** Featured Speaker 3 presentation\n* **12:15-2:00pm: VIP Lunch** (Vegetarian\, vegan and gluten-free options available)\n* **12:30-4:15pm:** BizX 2026 Expo\n* **2:30-3:00pm:** Featured Speaker 4 presentation\n* **4:30-5:00pm:** ***Awards ceremony*** >*BizX 2026 Expo Contest winners\, guest door prize draw\, exhibitor draw > **Great prizes to be won!***\n\n\\*Refreshments available all day – Coffee\, tea\, juice\, pop\, water\n\\*Snacks available until 4:15pm\n\n**VIP TICKETS:**\n\n* $59 regular or $49 until August 31\, 2026\n* Free for Mega\, Exhibitor and Referral Group members\n\n**Not a member?** Join us today >> https://gtapreneurs.com/business-networking-memberships\n\n**Book a vendor table:** Book now >> https://gtapreneurs.com/product/bizx-2025-exhibitor\n\n**Sponsor BizX 2025**\, send us a message >> info@gtapreneurs.com\n\n**SPONSORED BY:**\n\n* **Gorette Marques\,** Global Bricks Realty\, www.gmarquesrealtor.com\n* **Sonia Kurmey\,** Arbonne\, www.soniakurmey.arbonne.com\n* **Balbir Pabila\,** PPLSI\\~LegalShield\, https://bkpabila.ladiesofjustice.ca\n\n**DISCLAIMERS**\n\n***Event Photo and Video Disclaimer:*** By registering for and/or attending GTApreneurs (“Us” and “Our” and “We”) Events\, you give Us consent to use your image and/or video for Our publications\, advertising and/or other media activities (including the Internet).\n\n***Information Sharing:*** By registering for or attending a GTApreneurs networking event\, you are agreeing to share your name\, professional title\, organization name\, city\, website (if given) and LinkedIn URL (if given) with the other event attendees who attend that event. If you indicate in your registration form that you give Us permission to share your phone number and/or your email address with the other event attendees\, we will share the information you give Us permission to share. If you indicate in the registration form that you don’t give Us permission to share your phone number and/or your email address with the other attendees\, We will not share it with the other attendees. GTApreneurs will never share your home address with anyone.\n\n***Event Guest Contact Sheet:*** If you don’t attend an event\, you will not be given the guest contact sheet and your name or other information will not appear on the sheet.
